@startuml
scale 1.5
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #e3f2fd
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #1565c0

|Bruin pipeline|
|Outside Bruin|

|Bruin pipeline|
start
:Open Food Facts\n(parquet, 50K or 4.4M);
:**raw_products** (SQL)\nRead parquet over HTTPS\nFilter to valid grades;
note right: Quality checks:\nnot_null,\naccepted_values a-e
:**clean_products** (Python)\nPydantic validation\nReject bad rows, normalize types;

fork
  :**nutrition_summary** (SQL)\nGROUP BY nutriscore_grade;
  note right: Quality checks:\nunique, positive
fork again
  :**suspicious_products** (SQL)\nFlag grade/nutrition mismatches;
fork again
  :**product_embeddings** (Python)\nGitHub Models text-embedding-3-small\nStore vectors in DuckDB;
end fork

|Outside Bruin|
:**train_model.py**\nHistGradientBoosting\nPredict grade from nutrition\nConfusion matrix;
:**report.qmd** (Quarto)\nTables, charts, confusion matrix\nSimilar-product panel;
stop

@enduml
